00:29:07.220 --> 00:29:08.153
&gt;&gt; Where did you get your
idea for <i>Just Ella</i>?

00:29:09.220 --> 00:29:10.310
&gt;&gt; Margaret Peterson Haddix: Where
did I get my idea for <i>Just Ella</i>?

00:29:12.530 --> 00:29:12.890
Well that dates back to when
my daughter was really little

00:29:15.970 --> 00:29:16.740
and she's a senior in high school
now so this was many years ago

00:29:19.400 --> 00:29:22.666
and she was obsessed with
fairy tales when she was

00:29:22.730 --> 00:29:24.930
about two, three, four years old.

00:29:25.310 --> 00:29:25.673
And so she could sit there for hours
having me read fairly tales to her,

00:29:29.680 --> 00:29:30.900
which I was very proud that
she had such an attention span

00:29:32.260 --> 00:29:32.330
and I was glad that
she loved books already

00:29:34.990 --> 00:29:39.456
but reading those fairy tales to
her they started really bugging me.

00:29:39.920 --> 00:29:42.186
It really bugged me that it seemed

00:29:42.520 --> 00:29:45.453
like in every single
fairy tale I read to her

00:29:45.930 --> 00:29:50.063
at some point there could be a
sentence that was something like

00:29:50.160 --> 00:29:53.893
and then the prince took one
look at her and fell in love

00:29:55.800 --> 00:29:57.733
because she was so beautiful.

00:29:59.110 --> 00:30:02.243
And I felt like saying
to my daughter okay honey

00:30:03.470 --> 00:30:07.670
if this strange guy that you've
never met before comes up to you

00:30:07.960 --> 00:30:11.826
and gets down on bended knee
and says, "Will you marry me"?

00:30:12.130 --> 00:30:13.863
Do not say yes right away.

00:30:14.590 --> 00:30:15.003
If he seems like he might be a
decent guy, maybe you can say maybe

00:30:18.510 --> 00:30:18.920
but this whole love at first sight
idea was a little bit scarey.

00:30:22.300 --> 00:30:22.453
So writing <i>Just Ella</i> was kind
of my way of dealing with that

00:30:26.080 --> 00:30:27.923
and because I couldn't say all that
to my daughter when she was only two

00:30:28.970 --> 00:30:32.036
or three years old so I
wrote the book instead.

